ore":127},"full_slug_flat":"about/thomas-lattimore","active":true,"slug":"thomas-lattimore","parent":"34e0e09c-7246-4b53-ba45-b759a025d235","template":"profile","deck":"Thomas has been working with Drupal since 2009 and has strong experience with front-end development. ","position":"Front-end Developer","expertise":["Drupal Theming","Front-end Development"],"body":{"value":"\u003cp>Thomas began building websites with Drupal in 2009 when he was attracted to Drupal for it’s flexibility and vibrant community. He has been an active member of the Charlotte Drupal User Group since it began in Fall of 2010. Thomas’ contributions to the Drupal community include: presentations at numerous Drupal Camps and meetups, a number of theme related patches to Drupal 7 and 8 core, and contributions to several themes and modules on Drupal.org. Moving forward, Thomas also plans on experimenting with Node.js and AngularJS.\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp>Thomas Lattimore was born in a small town outside of Charlotte, North Carolina where he and his wife still reside. In his free time he enjoys spending time outdoors with his wife, playing music (guitar and drums).\u003c/p>\n","format":"filtered_html"},"quote_text":"","quote_cite":"","fact":"","time_zone":"America/New_York","location":"Charlotte, NC","promos":[],"links":{"drupalorg":"tlattimore","dribbble":"","facebook":"","flickr":"","github":"tlattimore","googlePlus":"","lanyrd":"","linkedIn":"","twitter":"tlattimore"},"external":[],"image":{"fid":"3408","uri":"bios/headshot_thomas.jpg","mime":"image/jpeg","alt":"","caption":"","title":""},"hero_image":{"fid":"3576","uri":"msp_1408_4134.jpg","mime":"image/jpeg","alt":"moss in the woods","caption":"","title":""},"hero_image_invert":true,"map":{"fid":"3030","uri":"maps/map_maggie-opt_0.svg","mime":"image/svg+xml","alt":"","caption":"","title":"","contents":"\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" version=\"1.1\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" viewBox=\"0 0 50.