 business ever since.\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp>Greg is also a world-class pinball player and has been participating in pinball tournaments for nearly 20 years. For some of his career he managed to marry his fascination with the game with his software engineering work, writing C++ code to run various games.\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp>His Drupal resume has included stints with leading Drupal agencies Palantir and NodeOne, and his body of work includes work for \u003cem>\u003ca href=\"http://www.foreignaffairs.com\">Foreign Affairs\u003c/a>\u003c/em> magazine, \u003ca href=\"http://ikea.com\">Ikea\u003c/a> and the Swedish Government. He authored Deploy module and was a long time maintainer of the Services module. He is also co-author of Packt's \"\u003ca href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Drupal-Module-Development-Matt-Butcher/dp/1849511160\">Drupal 7 Module Development\u003c/a>.\"\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp>Greg makes his home in Portland, OR with his girlfriend Nicole, their cat Faran, and their dog Guinnevere. In Portland he attempts to stay current with the Punk Rock scene. Says Greg, \"Some people find their Zen through meditation, I find mine getting crushed up against the stage in a mosh pit.\"\u003c/p>\n","format":"markdown"},"quote_text":"","quote_cite":"","fact":"Greg is 246th in the World Pinball Player Rankings.","time_zone":"America/Los_Angeles","location":"Portland, OR","promos":[],"links":{"drupalorg":"gdd","dribbble":"","facebook":"","flickr":"heyrocker","github":"heyrocker","googlePlus":"","lanyrd":"heyrocker","linkedIn":"","twitter":""},"external":[{"url":"http://www.amazon.com/Drupal-Module-Development-Matt-Butcher/dp/1849511160/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&ie=UTF8&qid=1435063437&sr=1-1","title":"Drupal Seven Module Development","type":"book","source":"Amazon.com"}],"image":{"fid":"3400","uri":"bios/headshot_greg.jpg","mime":"image/jpeg","alt":"","caption":"","title":""},"hero_image":{"fid":"2777","uri":"profile-hero-greg.jpg","mime":"image/jpeg","alt":"A close-up of a pinball machine